":1127223,"uid":12015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"去到絕望時即係無野再可以輸<br />\n盡情去做以前想做不敢做的事吧<br />\n你會覺得好爽好正<br />\n不過犯法事就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d026f9be979acb5cbcb205ea5a424333ecd9fb64","tid":1127223,"uid":241434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"我都好大壓力，一齊面對。<br />\n你諗到乜野方法走未？<br />\n講黎聽下，開心些牙啊！"},{"pid":"5665156fed6d17b072890938368535464da4dba7","tid":1127223,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a998679142568dfbfd59b8ad74e1707abd5b9cf2","tid":1127223,"uid":128498,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c2bffe999234a6547b6947028ec6de8e96d02823","tid":1127223,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"好大壓力？"},"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"感情 屋企人 事業<br />\n啲嘢多到唔識點講<br />\n我竟然一個月之內乜都冇晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:23:29.000Z","msg":"第一步要學識同人講自己嘅感受，同成件事嘅來龍去脈，未必有人解決到問題，年一可以減壓抒緩"},{"pid":"a6b877e70d5ef35f19dc4bc6c134ee4daef9137f","tid":1127223,"uid":182195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"講出黎想死唔容易，你一定係經歷好大壓力先講出口<br />\n但你要知道你要面對壓力嘅方法有好多，你有好多選擇"},{"pid":"4619774f52d58a402f74effb16b2d263c183d93a","tid":1127223,"uid":12909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a998679142568dfbfd59b8ad74e1707abd5b9cf2","tid":1127223,"uid":128498,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c2bffe999234a6547b6947028ec6de8e96d02823","tid":1127223,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"好大壓力？"},"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"感情 屋企人 事業<br />\n啲嘢多到唔識點講<br />\n我竟然一個月之內乜都冇晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"做咩會突然之間發生咁多事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主你身邊有冇人幫到你呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g